snippet.title: Sandbox Play - Trailer [0.5.3]
snippet.description:
Sandbox Play is a build and destroy sandbox game with no particular goal in mind. Your only job is to build whatever you want and watch it crumble.

It is available on the following 2 links:
http://gamejolt.com/games/sandbox-play/46322
https://slojanko.itch.io/sandbox-play

Song used:
 The Big Decision by Audionautix is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution license (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
Artist: http://audionautix.com/
